## Stage 5 — Thermal Model

### Two-State Lumped Thermal Model

```
C_core  dT_core/dt    = Q_gen - (T_core - T_surf) / R_c
C_surf  dT_surf/dt    = (T_core - T_surf)/R_c - (T_surf - T_amb)/R_u
```

### Heat Generation

```
Q_total = Q_ohmic + Q_entropic
Q_ohmic    = I² R(T)                         [irreversible]
Q_entropic = I T dU/dT                        [reversible]
R(T) = R_ref exp(Ea/R (1/T - 1/T_ref))       [Arrhenius]
```

---

## Stage 6 — Degradation

### SEI Growth (square-root law)

```
δ_SEI(t) = √(k_SEI × t × exp(-Ea/RT))
Q_loss_SEI = F aₛ δ_SEI c_SEI L A / 3600     [Ah]
```

### Empirical Capacity Fade

```
Q_loss(n) = A exp(-Ea/RT) × (I_rms/I_ref)^z × n^0.5
```

